k lives-eq/$1k · 9% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 63%&lt;br&gt;(Sam Peltzman, Luisa Rodriguez)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + resilience_undermines_deterrence&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Peltzman effect for civil defence: making nuclear war survivable weakens deterrence and raises the chance of war, so a resilient-food dollar partly insures against a catastrophe it also makes marginally likelier. An alternative, lower estimate for ALLFED, anchored to Rodriguez&#x27;s ~0.4%/yr US-Russia war probability. Requires future people to be in the circle. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtz2zYW%2FSt3PNtdKSvRJPW2151xYrnN1EkztrOdTpxRIBKSsKFILgBaUdL0t%2FcAJCXKlidM9UVDkcC55z5xL74chXzGski%2FSEJ%2BdHJ0fExnZ2d0K5mISScUSPZ5jYdVTHeZ73pdWiUyCu8FX9HKm%2FiT3qQ%2FGUyGE8%2BjhtJJSp7XNBB3MaDOlcqWqRZJTMECiCfkUspkEiwEiwygN%2FLJoxmTE7Zi68kiW7JYlR98YrFYskhNVLLkqwXT5ZcezTKdSV5smCyZ1lxOVkIvJqFQQZLFWsTzcnmf4qT6frKzu1w12Igr4NgkSjYih6Sy2YxLuz0JMsXDjQIeSa5EJHgc8EkWh1wuRczVJOSAkeattcaYBQtiW5MIRYzerPUCzzMRcYLJt5%2FVMWmjMgtD1YIA%2BMmAUiItmORtWJItjQih8F4veG7kfylYJw4sxikFyTJNlDHGZgH2Go5QQC%2BEsmhKszhkURJzWiIQIoc%2BbPw8vv9gqJrt%2FFPKA42N9yzKOCUzi7ANCceCPedK0zRbkzWF2ah4VbETOn9Jis24XlPjmoerJAnpGouYDBbNHOOn8evx9fnt%2BIKma5rzmEumuZOuyyjkodA7xnqGjy34WeeUjD2BZLHewgFSG8WXiUTcbeym8rW5UViawoPKoZv10omSeZxIBEPjS9prUTrqfW1aLOuzkfsDvXh5aldOuWb521QmUzZFGGgQmSZG%2BdCk0Du3Rd57hy5ZoBPIZDIPB4EFqfFErFukEuImPBI5h%2F%2FG71YX51e%2FH%2F%2FjPU15lKyQIWav9TP%2FhOdoje3Ahm0tFmSHWaBzj8CHHHEN9WdRkmHXAu6%2FKMKfzh4riLR03KFV0zwOvzaJbIgBEzqsuJgvgI0klpzZxFrAWiYaFTVukyVT4uMp%2FRcKmW%2B%2B67sw1iZd3kgB6vD1Xsme4xWC%2B06vEMw%2F