yrU%2BJJgVVel38dHXvwAGOgGP" id="w1_2_5_6_7_8_11"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1116" y="70" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Time of perils:&lt;br&gt;space settlement exits it&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8+11+14]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   930k lives-eq/$1k · 22% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 52%&lt;br&gt;(Toby Ord, Elon Musk)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + resilience_undermines_deterrence + time_of_perils_exit&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Time-of-perils optimism: hazard is high during the AI / nuclear transition but collapses once decorrelated, self-sufficient settlements exist — no single catastrophe reaches them all. The window closes, the expected future stretches far past the background-hazard baseline, and x-risk reduction during the window is what unlocks it (Ord, The Precipice; the multiplanetary-backup argument). Mutually exclusive with the view that early expansion re-arms the hazard. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 14 time_of_perils_exit" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6u3bUdyW8nmwHSxpkpNn0gSXcwaAqXlmibG1nSklQct9P57XtISrbcOIg6%2BRIoEnnuuU%2FeS389CPmMZZF%2BlYT84Ojg8JBOTk7oWjIRk04okOzLGg%2BrmG6ytud3aZXIKLwTfEUrf9Ke9Cb9yWAynPj%2BBB9rSicp%2Bd26QbmJgXaqVLZMtUhiChYAPSKPUiaTYCFYZDD9UZt8mjE5YSu2niyyJYtV8aFNLBZLFqmJSpZ8tWC6%2BNKjWaYzyfMNkyXTmsvJSujFJBQqSLJYi3heLO9TnJTfT3Z2F6sGG3E5HJtEyUbkkFQ2m3FptydBpni4UcAnyZWIBI8DPsnikMuliLmahBww0rzdLO2SFks%2BSWaTFFiQxe%2BFtrYas2BBbGswoYjR%2B7Ve4H