acAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtT20gW%2FSu3qJ1dm7GNZOMXLFNFgplJLclQQDY1FVJOW2pbvchqbbeEcTLJb9%2FTLcmWwRTKeL%2BkHEl97rnnPvp283XP51OWhslr6fO9o72DAzo5OaEbxUREiSRPsS9L%2FFhEdJu2HfeQFlKF%2Fr3gC1q44%2Fa4O%2B6N%2B%2BPB2HXHbnfs9qmmExmT268boNsIgKdap%2FM4ETIiLwDuETkUMyW9QLDQwLrDNrk0ZWrMFmw5DtI5i3Txok0sEnMW6rGWc74IWFK86dI0TVLF8wXjOUsSrsYLkQRjX2hPplEiolnxeY8iWX4%2B3lhdfNVfmcvh2DiUK5MD0ul0ypVdLr1Uc3%2FlgEuKaxEKHnl8nEY%2BV3MRcT32OWCUebr6tEs6ZviKP8QwDWHGE%2BbdTQUAVt%2F0KeZK4xWDQc8SNqpbRUfMC4itZRWaGF0ukwC%2FpyLkhOCtX%2BsDSoxszPd1AyQRcUOMpLJgijcRDTY3NIXG8yTgWaD%2BoaFw5FmMY%2FLkPJbaCLr6AGuNnxAhCYS2aDphkc9CGXGaI6XCFn1eZczo%2FrOhapbDcziFhfcsTDnJqUVYJ1fLgr3iOqFJuiQrp1moedmxI7oOlJjH9IGHSB9Ol0r%2BB7jZ6l9H70ZXpzejM5osacYjrljCW%2FGyyGTui2RDpn28bCBLkoyMURJIFus9wqcS4%2FJcKmTtSjGdfZvJweIY8dctul7OW6GcRVIhlWpf426D4mH3W91i2WgNnZ%2Fo9Ztj%2B%2BWEJyx7Gis5YRMkUQIiE2nc9k0ZfnQa5H5q0TnzEgmb8DWDwgexiUGUNEhL4iYxpJohcqOPi7PTiz8O%2FvaJJjyUC9SXWWsjzB%2FwO1xiObChqsWCbT%2F1kiwWiB5HasL9aShTrAoQ%2BLO8eOjkqYMo6pYzsG6an4NvdSKbXMCEDwsuZgGw0QIUZ7YsA6hl8lBT7UbOmRZ3x%2FRvOGTetZ22A7FWxXapBKgny%2B2W3ZabG%2B61urlh%2FpAoVjLL7hE%2FAw2feYQ0WmE%2Fbz5rECWvXQsd42EzEXNOP5PHEqYTJWMoZvpFlDJbkaYQmWpmCHmS167YXPPlwTXSJqLvzk8HS0X3mt5J5Qcs1fTdbXXNw2MYOkEeUtGtwGXdRd7x5C0atjCppp4LRSEIpMkF0YEpEAT39OLifHSGDJmgJKYoAZ2qe3Fv%2FC61Kq6kaUxUu%2BRh8gUd8piupK%2FELOVfwL11aNm%2Fv25epVoLKM1U%2FZhQISH94hZVjg4G2bVpBZCspJVuJrI5F4mYoSQhokYK2pb4Ku%2BDL3votFfJ1stdTNALjPIbDSYPwSIwfZEzhbRftV3T%2B5iaZ2QD9oUpn2pnPPUjvoRAfsrCZmpbDnSRwj%2BQaiISlL%2BIpsr4gnoB%2BDH6DzJZaXgUaMMgsPWmIPcUNrBAo0E1TcoJz2wQKD2NoM